Title: Heeeelllp!!!
Description:
Hey! You!

Get me down! Away from these worms! Please!

I'll pay you! I'll even owe you one! Heck, I'll gladly sell out any cartel member you need dirt on! 

Just get me down!

Also, don't walk too much. They can hear your footsteps. Move from rock to rock if you don't want a swarm coming after you.
PortraitGiverText: An opportunist in way over her head.
